Most agents are graded at the end.  Pass/fail, resolved/abandoned.

@GetCandidly built something different: a model that reads the conversation while it's happening and steers toward resolution in real time.

Full story: https://t.co/mTxacVG2hI https://t.co/EcjvvsCzNk

Selling a membership or closing a car sale? Outcome-based pricing makes sense. The value is real and measurable.

Answering a knowledge lookup? Usage-based is simpler and probably right.

@zackrw from @SierraPlatform on how AI pricing should actually map to value delivered. https://t.co/XveYoWBP6e
